# Auth Module Patterns

## Form Structure
- **Base Layout:** All auth forms should use the pattern from [login-form.tsx](mdc:src/components/login-form.tsx)
- **Container:** `<div className="flex min-h-svh w-full items-center justify-center p-6 md:p-10 bg-background">`
- **Form Wrapper:** `<div className={cn("flex flex-col gap-6", className)}>`
- **Language Switcher:** Always include at the top right

## Form Components
- **Card Structure:** Use CardHeader, CardContent, and optionally CardFooter
- **Form Spacing:** Use `className="space-y-6"` for form fields
- **Button Styling:** Full width buttons with loading states
- **Link Styling:** Use brand primary color with hover effects

## Error Handling
- **Error Colors:** Use `text-destructive` for error messages
- **Success States:** Use `text-success` for success messages
- **Loading States:** Show loading text with `text-muted-foreground`

## Navigation Links
- **Pattern:** `text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline underline-offset-4 transition-colors`
- **Consistency:** All auth forms should have consistent navigation patterns

## Validation
- Use translated validation messages from `useTranslations`
- Implement proper form state management with disabled states
- Follow patterns from [reset-password-form.tsx](mdc:src/components/reset-password-form.tsx)
